OL,3,CDad who's raised millions for life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment wins Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAward
OL,7,FOur presenter Amy Lea surprised our
OL,8,Fwinner Sergio Petrucci today
OL,10,FA Sunderland dad who has raised
OL,11,Fmillions for cardiac equipment off the
OL,12,Fback of his daughter's own life-saving
OL,13,Fheart surgery, will represent the ITV
OL,14,FTyne Tees region at the Pride of
OL,15,FBritain awards after winning the
OL,16,Fregional Fundraiser of the Year award.
