OL,4,Csaving equipment wins Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAward
OL,7,FSergio Petrucci, from Sunderland, set
OL,8,Fup a cardiac care charity in a bid to
OL,9,Fshow his thanks to the medical
OL,10,Fprofessionals who operated on his
OL,11,Fdaughter Luna in 2015.
OL,13,FThe Red Sky Foundation has since
OL,14,Fraised millions of pounds and provided
OL,15,Fhundreds of defibrillators in the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,18,FOn winning his award he said: "I have
OL,19,Fthe most amazing people and team,
OL,20,Fthey're more of an army.
