OL,7,F"It's everybody, it's a team effort
OL,8,Fand I hope that one day other people
OL,9,Fcan be inspired."
OL,11,FX Factor winner Joseph McElderry was
OL,12,Fpart of the judging panel and offered
OL,13,Fspecial praise to Mr Petrucci for his
OL,14,Fefforts.
OL,16,FHe said: "I think the thing Sergio has
OL,17,Fdone and the scale that he's done it
OL,18,Fat is so incredible.
