OL,7,F"The thought that's gone into not only
OL,8,Fproviding the defibrillators and kind
OL,9,Fof the immediate response kit to
OL,10,Fhelping somebody with a heart attack,
OL,11,Fbut also the bereavement counselling
OL,12,Fand the mental health help that he's
OL,13,Foffering from the other side of things
OL,14,Fthat people might not think about.
OL,16,F"I think it's two completely different
OL,17,Fthings that he's managed to do and the
OL,18,Fscale of that is incredible."
