OL,4,Csaving equipment wins Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAward
OL,7,FMr Petrucci's daughter Luna was born
OL,8,Fwith two holes in her heart. Just
OL,9,Fbefore her second birthday, doctors
OL,10,Fsaid it was now or never - she needed
OL,11,Fopen heart surgery.
OL,13,FOn the morning Luna was wheeled off
OL,14,Ffor treatment at Newcastle's Freeman
OL,15,FHospital, the sky blazed red -
OL,16,Finspiring the name of the charity the
OL,17,Ffather would go on to found with his
OL,18,Fwife Emma in 2020.
