OL,3,CDad who's raised millions for life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment wins Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAward
OL,7,FIt has since raised more than #2m,
OL,8,Fdonated more than 700 defibrillators,
OL,9,Ffunded machines that have conducted in
OL,10,Fexcess of 800 brain and heart scans
OL,11,Fevery year, and educated people of all
OL,12,Fages on the importance of CPR.
OL,14,FFive years down the line and its work
OL,15,Fis still paying off - giving others
OL,16,Fthat vital second chance at life.
OL,18,FThree years ago, a healthy Craig
OL,19,FHanson suffered cardiac arrest and
OL,20,Fcollapsed in his own home.
