OL,7,FA neighbour rushed to his aid and
OL,8,Fdelivered CPR - another fetching a
OL,9,Fnearby defibrillator - funded by Mr
OL,10,FPetrucci - which ultimately saved his
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F"I received two blasts from the
OL,14,Fmachine and it restarted my heart,"
OL,15,Fsaid Mr Hanson.
OL,17,F"I wasn't really aware, although I
OL,18,Fmust have walked past that
OL,19,Fdefibrillator hundreds of times, and
OL,20,Fnot realised the importance of it -
OL,21,Fnow obviously I do."
